description:
> `Description`: `download one` 

This endpoint allows downloading a file with the given [STUDY_ID] and [FILE_ID] as the request parameter.Ensure the JWT token is refreshed, before accessing this endpoint.

> `Request`: (Http Method: [GET]) https://cans.cachet.dk:443/api/studies/{{STUDY_ID}}/files/{{FILE_ID}}/download

This request must be authenticated using a HTTP OAuth 2.0 Authentication header.

> `Response`:

- On success returns a file content.
- If the JWT token is not refreshed, this would result in failure ’403’ (internal error).
- On failure status code `400` (bad request) is returned.
- On failure status code `401` (unauthorized) is returned.
- On failure status code `500` (internal server error) is returned.
